sub_title: Co-founder Foundation: Stichting Griekse Cultuur Filotechnia
summary:
Experience in:
- Multicultural, multinational programs.
- Dutch Press and Media.
- Organisation of events. 
- Board member in charge of cultural affairs in the Greek Community of The Hague.
- Organising International Congresses, Events, Exhibitions in Museums, International Organisations and Galleries in Greece and in the Netherlands.
- European programs, writing and publishing of teaching books, teaching experience in the secondary education. 
- Archaeological excavations, archive organisation and laboratory analysis of findings in Greece and in France.
